00:22:48,560 --> 00:22:49,500
 u svoje misli,

435
00:22:49,500 --> 00:22:50,320
 čuju,

436
00:22:50,320 --> 00:22:51,320
 to bi napravla to,

437
00:22:51,320 --> 00:22:53,300
 od stvari za kuću

438
00:22:53,300 --> 00:22:55,460
 do evangelizacijskih stvari,

439
00:22:55,460 --> 00:22:56,400
 do projekata.

440
00:22:57,060 --> 00:22:57,680
 ono, ja kažem,

441
00:22:57,680 --> 00:22:58,300
 aha, aha,

442
00:22:58,300 --> 00:22:59,760
 super, super.

443
00:22:59,760 --> 00:23:03,240
 Ojeje, kako ti se sviđa o pjesmu?

444
00:23:03,240 --> 00:23:04,400
 Sada snimamo pjesmu,

445
00:23:04,400 --> 00:23:04,860
 spot.

446
00:23:04,860 --> 00:23:06,820
 Čuj, šta misliš ljubavi o ome?

447
00:23:06,820 --> 00:23:07,840
 Znači, mene maja žena

448
00:23:07,840 --> 00:23:09,360
 hoće uključiti čista srca.

449
00:23:09,360 --> 00:23:11,920
 Ona meni daje poštovanje

450
00:23:11,920 --> 00:23:13,120
 kad mi kaže,

451
00:23:13,120 --> 00:23:14,320
 šta ti misliš o ome?

452
00:23:14,320 --> 00:23:16,340
 Prvo mene pita.

453
00:23:17,860 --> 00:23:18,700
 A ja kažem,

454
00:23:18,700 --> 00:23:19,140
 super,

455
00:23:19,140 --> 00:23:19,600
 ko je?

456
00:23:19,600 --> 00:23:21,220
 I negdje u svoju,

457
00:23:21,220 --> 00:23:21,460
 ono,

458
00:23:21,460 --> 00:23:22,780
 uzivam obitelj nešto,

459
00:23:22,780 --> 00:23:24,280
 pa mislim kao nešto,

460
00:23:24,280 --> 00:23:25,020
 brinem se,

461
00:23:25,020 --> 00:23:26,880
 imam svojih briga.

462
00:23:26,880 --> 00:23:29,420
 Još mi sad i ona mora,

463
00:23:29,420 --> 00:23:29,760
 ona, jel?

464
00:23:29,760 --> 00:23:30,720
 Dakle,

465
00:23:30,720 --> 00:23:33,140
 i to mi gospodin to pokazuje,

466
00:23:33,140 --> 00:23:34,020
 razgoličuje me.

467
00:23:34,020 --> 00:23:36,420
 I ona mi gospodin dao milost

468
00:23:36,420 --> 00:23:39,600
 da kad mi otvorio oči,

469
00:23:39,600 --> 00:23:42,200
 da sam pao na koljena,

470
00:23:42,200 --> 00:23:42,920
 proplako,

471
00:23:42,920 --> 00:23:45,060
 ušao kajanje

472
00:23:45,060 --> 00:23:47,160
 i zamolio Boga za oprost.

473
00:23:47,860 --> 00:23:49,180
 Zamolio Boga za oprost.

474
00:23:49,180 --> 00:23:50,760
 Gospodine, oprosti mi,

475
00:23:50,760 --> 00:23:53,380
 ozdravi u meni

476
00:23:53,380 --> 00:23:55,260
 to što je bolestno.

477
00:23:55,260 --> 00:23:57,480
 Ozdravi u meni

478
00:23:57,480 --> 00:23:58,180
 taj,

479
00:23:58,180 --> 00:23:59,600
 tu potrebu

480
00:23:59,600 --> 00:24:02,180
 da iako sam u obitelji,

481
00:24:02,180 --> 00:24:03,780
 prisutan sam u kući,

482
00:24:03,780 --> 00:24:06,020
 bježim iz obitelji.

483
00:24:06,020 --> 00:24:07,300
 Tu sam,

484
00:24:07,300 --> 00:24:08,980
 ali ne do kraja.

485
00:24:08,980 --> 00:24:11,040
 I to se osjeti.

486
00:24:11,040 --> 00:24:12,520
 Ljubav,

487
00:24:12,520 --> 00:24:13,880
 kad nije do kraja

488
00:24:13,880 --> 00:24:14,660
 izražena,

489
00:24:14,660 --> 00:24:15,500
 nas se osjeti.

490
00:24:15,500 --> 00:24:16,960
 Ona vrijeđa,

491
00:24:16,960 --> 00:24:17,520
 po meni,

492
00:24:17,680 --> 00:24:18,500
 puno puta

493
00:24:18,500 --> 00:24:20,140
 više

494
00:24:20,140 --> 00:24:20,740
 nego

495
00:24:20,740 --> 00:24:23,480
 da si grup,

496
00:24:23,480 --> 00:24:24,760
 da nema ono,

497
00:24:24,760 --> 00:24:26,180
 da nema ljubavi.

498
00:24:26,180 --> 00:24:27,220
 Onda ljudi znaju

499
00:24:27,220 --> 00:24:28,240
 na čem se ovakve,

500
00:24:28,240 --> 00:24:29,200
 ovakve ubije to,

501
00:24:29,200 --> 00:24:31,060
 ta neizainteresiranost.

502
00:24:31,060 --> 00:24:33,200
 To ubija.

503
00:24:33,200 --> 00:24:34,080
 To ubija.

504
00:24:34,080 --> 00:24:37,440
 I ulazim u to iskustvo,

505
00:24:37,440 --> 00:24:38,160
 molim,

506
00:24:38,160 --> 00:24:38,980
 plaćem,

507
00:24:38,980 --> 00:24:40,680
 kajem se

508
00:24:40,680 --> 00:24:42,140
 i gospodine,

509
00:24:42,140 --> 00:24:42,780
 nešto radi.

510
00:24:42,780 --> 00:24:43,500
 Šta radi?

511
00:24:43,500 --> 00:24:45,360
 Počinje mijenjati moje srce

512
00:24:45,360 --> 00:24:47,820
 i počinje čistiti moje srce.

513
00:24:47,820 --> 00:24:49,560
 Čistiti moju ljubav.

514
00:24:49,560 --> 00:24:52,220
 Šta je,

515
00:24:52,220 --> 00:24:53,840
 koje će biti cilj

516
00:24:53,840 --> 00:24:55,560
 nas u Kakao Desu

517
00:24:55,560 --> 00:24:57,760
 u sljedećih četiri godine?

518
00:24:59,960 --> 00:25:02,380
 Koje će biti naše temeljne oružje

519
00:25:02,380 --> 00:25:03,560
 s kojim ćemo ići naprijed?

520
00:25:03,560 --> 00:25:06,260
 Pa ja vjerujem da će to biti ljubav.

521
00:25:06,260 --> 00:25:08,060
 Ljubav prije svega.

522
00:25:08,060 --> 00:25:10,020
 Ljubav.

523
00:25:10,020 --> 00:25:14,440
 Ljubav mijenja u evangelizaciji ljudska srca,

524
00:25:14,440 --> 00:25:16,620
 a čuda mijenjaju um.

525
00:25:16,620 --> 00:25:20,140
 Mi puno puta tražimo

526
00:25:20,140 --> 00:25:21,960
 da nam gospodin da dar ozdravljenja,

527
00:25:21,960 --> 00:25:24,020
 dar spoznaje,

528
00:25:24,020 --> 00:25:24,960
 čuda nekih.

529
00:25:24,960 --> 00:25:27,920
 Ali ne tražimo ljubav dublju

530
00:25:27,920 --> 00:25:29,060
 i ne radimo na njoj.

531
00:25:29,420 --> 00:25:30,680
 da upoštamo gospodinu

532
00:25:30,680 --> 00:25:32,100
 da se ljubav razvija

533
00:25:32,100 --> 00:25:33,040
 kroz čišćenje,

534
00:25:33,040 --> 00:25:36,320
 kroz iskustvo nemoći i pada našega.

535
00:25:36,320 --> 00:25:38,280
 Evo,

536
00:25:38,280 --> 00:25:39,840
 jedan primjer.

537
00:25:39,840 --> 00:25:43,180
 Moj brat Matija Kopić

538
00:25:43,180 --> 00:25:46,380
 zamolio me prije dvije godine

539
00:25:46,380 --> 00:25:48,600
 da mu pomognem u njegovoj firmi,

540
00:25:48,600 --> 00:25:50,880
 da se brinem za ljude,

541
00:25:50,880 --> 00:25:55,860
 za, kako se to kaže u poslovnom svijetu,

542
00:25:55,860 --> 00:25:58,060
 mentalno zdravlje.

543
00:25:58,880 --> 00:26:00,140
 i

544
00:26:00,140 --> 00:26:04,700
 a ovoga on i ja znamo da je to duševrižništvo.

545
00:26:04,700 --> 00:26:08,360
 I okej, stvarno bio sam tamo ljudima na raspolaganju,

546
00:26:08,360 --> 00:26:10,220
 doktorima,

547
00:26:10,220 --> 00:26:11,780
 znanosti,

548
00:26:11,780 --> 00:26:13,940
 jako, jako pametnim tipovima

549
00:26:13,940 --> 00:26:19,400
 za koje se svjetske firme otimaju na tjednoj razini.

550
00:26:21,400 --> 00:26:23,260
 doći pred njih,

551
00:26:23,260 --> 00:26:24,580
 to su ljudi koji su ateisti,

552
00:26:24,580 --> 00:26:26,160
 najčešće,

553
00:26:26,160 --> 00:26:27,820
 doći pred njih

554
00:26:27,820 --> 00:26:31,600
 i kad se neka otvori pričaj o smislu života,

555
00:26:31,600 --> 00:26:34,560
 nakon što porazgovaramo o stanju u njihovom timu

556
00:26:34,560 --> 00:26:36,320
 ili u stanju njih osobno,

557
00:26:36,320 --> 00:26:37,440
 ono,

558
00:26:37,440 --> 00:26:39,560
 to je, ono,

559
00:26:39,560 --> 00:26:40,760
 bog nigdje ne postoji.

560
00:26:40,760 --> 00:26:42,480
 Oni se klanjuju svojome razumu,

561
00:26:42,480 --> 00:26:44,380
 klanjuju se svoj inteligenciji,

562
00:26:44,380 --> 00:26:45,520
 moćni su,

563
00:26:45,520 --> 00:26:46,400
 imaju novaca,

564
00:26:46,400 --> 00:26:47,160
 lijepi su,

565
00:26:47,160 --> 00:26:48,160
 markantni su,

566
00:26:48,480 --> 00:26:49,580
 i sjeti me pod nogama.

567
00:26:49,580 --> 00:26:52,360
 No postoji fora,

568
00:26:52,360 --> 00:26:55,200
 ja kad god bi išao iz Osijeka za Zagreb,

569
00:26:55,200 --> 00:26:57,420
 ja bih svek molio

570
00:26:57,420 --> 00:27:00,180
 i prikazivao sve te ljude po imenu gospodino.

571
00:27:00,180 --> 00:27:05,280
 Onda bi mi ponekad gospodin za neke određene ljude dao jasnoću

572
00:27:05,280 --> 00:27:06,440
 s čim se bore,

573
00:27:06,440 --> 00:27:08,280
 s čim se muče

574
00:27:08,280 --> 00:27:11,040
 i dao mi do znanja,

575
00:27:11,040 --> 00:27:11,340
 pardon,

576
00:27:11,340 --> 00:27:14,280
 da im to, ono, mogu reći

577
00:27:14,280 --> 00:27:17,860
 i da će se tu dogoditi otvaranje njihovog srca i otvaranje uma.

578
00:27:18,480 --> 00:27:21,460
 I zaista, to bi tako bilo.

579
00:27:21,460 --> 00:27:25,260
 Ti ljudi su znali stati

580
00:27:25,260 --> 00:27:27,040
 i kapitulirati

581
00:27:27,040 --> 00:27:30,360
 pred jasnoćom da je Bog živ

582
00:27:30,360 --> 00:27:32,440
 kroz neku spoznoju

583
00:27:32,440 --> 00:27:34,200
 u kojim je gospodin dao njima stanje,

584
00:27:34,200 --> 00:27:35,160
 u kojem se nalaze

585
00:27:35,160 --> 00:27:37,520
 i konkretno vrlo jasno s čim se muče.

586
00:27:37,520 --> 00:27:39,380
 Ja su oni,

587
00:27:39,380 --> 00:27:40,880
 a svi su, inače,

588
00:27:40,880 --> 00:27:42,160
 bitna stvar,

589
00:27:42,160 --> 00:27:43,520
 svi su znali da sam vjernik.

590
00:27:43,520 --> 00:27:47,500
 Ja kad sam došao pomoći mati u Gideonu,

591
00:27:47,500 --> 00:27:48,900
 ja sam Matije rekao,

592
00:27:48,900 --> 00:27:50,340
 ja sam ne želim sakrivat.

593
00:27:50,340 --> 00:27:52,040
 Znači, ja, ono,

594
00:27:52,040 --> 00:27:53,960
 jasno je da neću mahat Biblijom

595
00:27:53,960 --> 00:27:54,940
 u firmi,

596
00:27:54,940 --> 00:27:57,680
 niti Matija bi sumnio da bi napreku gluposti

597
00:27:57,680 --> 00:27:58,500
 da se poznajemo,

598
00:27:58,500 --> 00:28:00,040
 ali ja sam rekao,

599
00:28:00,040 --> 00:28:00,760
 čuj, ono,

600
00:28:00,760 --> 00:28:02,880
 u toj prezentaciji

601
00:28:02,880 --> 00:28:04,440
 mojih nekih

602
00:28:04,440 --> 00:28:06,940
 komunikativnih vještina

603
00:28:06,940 --> 00:28:08,380
 koju ja trebam ponuditi

604
00:28:08,380 --> 00:28:09,160
 tvojim ljudima,

605
00:28:09,160 --> 00:28:10,800
 ja mislim da je pošteno,

606
00:28:10,800 --> 00:28:12,820
 da oni znaju da sam ja vjernik.

607
00:28:12,820 --> 00:28:14,600
 Vjerojatno će me googlat nešto

608
00:28:14,600 --> 00:28:17,480
 i vidjet će tamo svjedočanstva,

609
00:28:17,480 --> 00:28:18,200
 svašta nešto

610
00:28:18,200 --> 00:28:18,600
 i ono,

611
00:28:18,600 --> 00:28:19,020
 to je to.

612
00:28:19,020 --> 00:28:19,860
 Jel ti to u redu?

613
00:28:19,860 --> 00:28:20,400
 U redu je,

614
00:28:20,400 --> 00:28:21,120
 slobodno reci.

615
00:28:21,780 --> 00:28:23,600
 Tako su oni svi znali da sam ja vjernik.

616
00:28:23,600 --> 00:28:26,920
 I onda tu se počeo otvarati njihov um.

617
00:28:26,920 --> 00:28:28,660
 Počeli su kapitulirati

618
00:28:28,660 --> 00:28:29,680
 i rekli su,

619
00:28:29,680 --> 00:28:31,220
 okej, ovo ne možemo objasniti.

620
00:28:31,220 --> 00:28:32,820
 Ovdje nešto postoji.

621
00:28:32,820 --> 00:28:33,660
 Ali,

622
00:28:33,660 --> 00:28:36,000
 da se vratim na temo obitelji,

623
00:28:36,000 --> 00:28:37,280
 to ih nije promijenilo.

624
00:28:37,280 --> 00:28:38,860
 Znate šta ih je promijenilo?

625
00:28:38,860 --> 00:28:41,080
 Šta je promijenilo njihova srca

626
00:28:41,080 --> 00:28:42,200
 do dana današnje,

627
00:28:42,200 --> 00:28:43,140
 kad više ne radim,

628
00:28:43,140 --> 00:28:44,220
 da se čujem sa njima

629
00:28:44,220 --> 00:28:46,740
 i ti ljudi žele da imamo razgovore,

630
00:28:46,740 --> 00:28:48,100
 žele da se družimo,

631
00:28:48,100 --> 00:28:50,880
 da imamo jedno bratsko ozrače sada.

632
00:28:51,780 --> 00:28:54,900
 Njihova srca je počela mijati ljubav.

633
00:28:54,900 --> 00:28:59,400
 Oni su vidjeli mene da razgovaram sa njima

634
00:28:59,400 --> 00:29:01,240
 sa jednakom pažnjom

635
00:29:01,240 --> 00:29:04,200
 i ljubavlju i interesiranjem,

636
00:29:04,200 --> 00:29:06,520
 kao što razgovaram sa Matijom,

637
00:29:06,520 --> 00:29:08,500
 koji je CEO bio firme.

638
00:29:08,500 --> 00:29:14,200
 Vidjeli su da razgovaram sa kršćanima

639
00:29:14,200 --> 00:29:15,380
 u toj firmi,

640
00:29:15,380 --> 00:29:19,060
 s kojima sam krenio u neku molitvena aktivnosti,

641
00:29:19,060 --> 00:29:21,600
 da razgovaram sa istom ljubavlju

642
00:29:21,600 --> 00:29:23,060
 i sa bratom kršćenom

643
00:29:23,060 --> 00:29:24,920
 s kojime veže Isus Kristi,

644
00:29:24,920 --> 00:29:26,020
 oni to drugi znaju,

645
00:29:26,020 --> 00:29:30,220
 da nema drugog mog pogleda,

646
00:29:30,220 --> 00:29:31,300
 druge geste,

647
00:29:31,300 --> 00:29:33,020
 druge boje glasa.

648
00:29:33,020 --> 00:29:35,180
 Nema, kad razgovaram sa njima,

649
00:29:35,180 --> 00:29:36,220
 identičan sam.

650
00:29:36,220 --> 00:29:37,300
 Sjeđam se,

651
00:29:37,300 --> 00:29:38,980
 rekao sam gospodinu,

652
00:29:38,980 --> 00:29:43,340
 ako je to tvoj glas u mome srcu,

653
00:29:43,340 --> 00:29:44,660
 ako to ti govoriš,

654
00:29:44,660 --> 00:29:45,820
 ako to ti želiš,

655
00:29:45,820 --> 00:29:47,140
 razumski znam,

656
00:29:47,140 --> 00:29:48,120
 to je najbolje za mene.

657
00:29:49,600 --> 00:29:51,520
 i pristajem na to,

658
00:29:51,520 --> 00:29:52,060
 hoću,

659
00:29:52,060 --> 00:29:53,340
 ali bojim se.

660
00:29:53,340 --> 00:29:57,600
 I sjećam se da sam fizičku bol na srcu osjetio.

661
00:29:57,600 --> 00:29:59,100
 Baš bol na srcu,

662
00:29:59,100 --> 00:30:00,000
 stezanje,

663
00:30:00,000 --> 00:30:02,020
 pulsiranje srca,

664
00:30:02,020 --> 00:30:02,860
 stezanje,

665
00:30:02,940 --> 00:30:03,640
 puštanje,

666
00:30:03,640 --> 00:30:04,280
 stezanje,

667
00:30:04,280 --> 00:30:05,740
 kao da neki kamen otišao.

668
00:30:05,740 --> 00:30:07,840
 Proplakao sam još malo,

669
00:30:07,840 --> 00:30:09,240
 baš ja volim plakat,

670
00:30:09,240 --> 00:30:11,860
 kao ovoga veliki motivac i romantičar,

671
00:30:11,860 --> 00:30:17,500
 i nakon toga ušla jedna takva sloboda o mene.

672
00:30:17,500 --> 00:30:19,360
 Ja vam to ne mogu opisati.

673
00:30:19,360 --> 00:30:21,280
 Od toga dana,

674
00:30:21,280 --> 00:30:24,220
 stvari su drugačije.

675
00:30:25,520 --> 00:30:27,940
 To je jedna korist za mene,

676
00:30:27,940 --> 00:30:29,520
 korist za evangelizatora,

677
00:30:29,520 --> 00:30:35,240
 žrvanj obiteljskog života koji mijenja srce i pročišćava ljubav.

678
00:30:35,740 --> 00:30:38,840
 Idemo sad kratko samo kakve koristi zajednica ima od toga.

679
00:30:38,840 --> 00:30:44,620
 Najčešće zajednica onaka je kakav je voditelj zajednica.

680
00:30:44,620 --> 00:30:49,780
 Ako ja imam određene kreposti,

681
00:30:49,780 --> 00:30:52,120
 temeljne životne vrijednosti,

682
00:30:52,120 --> 00:30:54,420
 ako imam zdravu komunikaciju,

683
00:30:54,420 --> 00:30:57,380
 jasnoću po nekim bitnim pitanjima,

684
00:30:57,380 --> 00:30:58,880
 zajednica to uzima.

685
00:30:58,880 --> 00:31:01,020
 Kao djeca što uzimaju od oca i majke.

686
00:31:01,020 --> 00:31:02,720
 Isto tako,

687
00:31:02,720 --> 00:31:03,800
 ranjenosti

688
00:31:03,800 --> 00:31:06,920
 voditelja zajednice prelaze na zajednicu.

689
00:31:06,920 --> 00:31:09,200
 U ovom slučaju,

690
00:31:09,200 --> 00:31:11,020
 kada mi ulazimo u slobodu

691
00:31:11,020 --> 00:31:14,380
 od evangelizacije

692
00:31:14,380 --> 00:31:15,960
 kroz tamo vlastite

693
00:31:15,960 --> 00:31:17,540
 bijede,

694
00:31:17,540 --> 00:31:19,200
 iskustvo vlastite bijede,

695
00:31:19,200 --> 00:31:20,620
 zapravo

696
00:31:20,620 --> 00:31:23,680
 mi vam počinjemo živjeti

697
00:31:23,680 --> 00:31:24,560
 ono što je za mene

698
00:31:24,560 --> 00:31:27,100
 jako, jako lijepo, divno.

699
00:31:27,100 --> 00:31:29,320
 To mi u svetoj obitelji zaista živimo.

700
00:31:29,320 --> 00:31:31,940
 Imamo tu milost i sretnjstvo zbog toga.

701
00:31:31,940 --> 00:31:33,680
 Dolazimo do toga

702
00:31:33,680 --> 00:31:34,680
 da

703
00:31:34,680 --> 00:31:39,600
 čovjek je uvijek ispred zajednice.

704
00:31:39,600 --> 00:31:41,700
 Čovjek je ispred zajednice.

705
00:31:41,700 --> 00:31:42,740
 Znači,

706
00:31:42,740 --> 00:31:45,460
 prilazimo ljudima u zajednici

707
00:31:45,460 --> 00:31:47,880
 kada dolaze nova garnitura djece.

708
00:31:47,880 --> 00:31:49,580
 Evo, morate jednu stvar znati za zajednicu.

709
00:31:49,580 --> 00:31:52,200
 Čisto vam bude možda ova priča malo smislenija.

710
00:31:53,260 --> 00:32:04,920
 naši najaktivniji članovi zajednice svi su ljudi, muži, žena, oboje su zajednici, dakle parovi koji imaju mnogobrojnu obitelj, znači više djece.

711
00:32:05,040 --> 00:32:16,040
 I nama svako malo, sad zamislite, imate udarne ljude, evo jedno djete, drugo, treće, četvrto, peto, non stop djeca.

712
00:32:16,660 --> 00:32:17,620
 Male su razlike.

713
00:32:17,620 --> 00:32:23,720
 I, pazi, ti imaš jedan realan problem da ne možeš raditi neki iću neki bum.

714
00:32:23,720 --> 00:32:30,040
 Mi smo ciljano stali sa radom sa mladima, jer smo bili odgovorni prema njima i ponizni.

715
00:32:30,040 --> 00:32:34,200
 I znali smo, imamo metode kako ih možemo zapaliti, imamo iskustvo.

716
00:32:34,200 --> 00:32:36,300
 Ali ko će se brinit sa njima?

717
00:32:36,300 --> 00:32:40,040
 Pa ko ja nisam poravnat sa Rafaelom, Terezom i Rahelom i Dajanom.

718
00:32:40,040 --> 00:32:42,160
 Ko će se brinit za ove?

719
00:32:42,160 --> 00:32:43,320
 Pa uništitit ću ih.

720
00:32:43,320 --> 00:32:47,580
 Oni će tražit nas, naše vrijeme, a moji ljudi im to ne mogu dati.

721
00:32:47,580 --> 00:32:49,980
 Čekat ćemo, staćemo.

722
00:32:49,980 --> 00:32:53,720
 Uglavnom, naši primjeri.

723
00:32:53,720 --> 00:33:01,840
 Ajde, dolazi novo djete, kažeš voditi u nekoga tima, preduhitriš ga, pomažeš mu,

724
00:33:01,840 --> 00:33:07,060
 da samo ne mora ja da na početku crljiti kako da to kaže, da će se povuć,

725
00:33:07,060 --> 00:33:09,020
 a tamo smo ušli neki projekt.

726
00:33:09,020 --> 00:33:13,900
 Evo, a Bog mu je poremetio taj projekt, da ušli mu djete.

727
00:33:13,900 --> 00:33:18,080
 Čuj, brate, ajde šibaj doma.

728
00:33:18,080 --> 00:33:19,260
 Šibaj doma.

729
00:33:19,260 --> 00:33:20,880
 Budi doma sa svojom obitelji.

730
00:33:20,880 --> 00:33:23,360
 Budi u svoju ženu.

731
00:33:23,360 --> 00:33:28,360
 Kad ti se djete rodi, budi onoliko koliko je potrebno.

732
00:33:29,540 --> 00:33:32,080
 I ne samo to, šta mogu učinjen za tebe?

733
00:33:32,080 --> 00:33:34,200
 Kako ti mogu pomoći?

734
00:33:34,200 --> 00:33:36,500
 Jel ti treba šta?

735
00:33:36,500 --> 00:33:43,200
 Mi smo sebi kupovali, kad su naše žene trudne, idemo u nabavke, šopinge,

736
00:33:43,200 --> 00:33:45,100
 donosimo ručkove jedne drugima.

737
00:33:45,100 --> 00:33:49,040
 To su take geste ljubavi koje vas izuvaju iz cipela.

738
00:33:49,040 --> 00:33:51,280
 Izuvaju vas iz cipela.

739
00:33:51,280 --> 00:33:56,680
 Kad je moja žena ležala, moja majka je živa, i njena je mama živa,

740
00:33:56,680 --> 00:34:00,720
 i roditelji su na živi, imamo pomoć, stvarno smo tu blagostavljeni.

741
00:34:00,720 --> 00:34:05,240
 Ali uz njih tebi dođe zajednica, braća, sestre, muški,

742
00:34:05,240 --> 00:34:08,360
 donosi ručak, evo buraz, evo.

743
00:34:08,360 --> 00:34:10,320
 Evo košara, voča, evo, evo ono.

744
00:34:10,320 --> 00:34:11,780
 Pa ne treba buraz.

745
00:34:11,780 --> 00:34:19,820
 Pa to ubija, to razvara, ono, tvrdo ljudsko srce i mijenja te.

746
00:34:20,880 --> 00:34:24,840
 I što se događa takim pristupom, kad tako pristupamo,

747
00:34:24,840 --> 00:34:27,680
 kad smo tako pristupali našim ljudima,

748
00:34:27,680 --> 00:34:32,480
 zanimljivo je da, znate kako na početku malo,

749
00:34:32,480 --> 00:34:34,720
 tako i naravno i kod nas bilo, malo ljudi pobjegnu,

750
00:34:34,720 --> 00:34:39,100
 dođe prvo djete, pa si uplašen, pa si fokusiran skroz na njega,

751
00:34:39,100 --> 00:34:42,540
 pa ga držiš za sebe, ko malo zlatno tele,

752
00:34:42,540 --> 00:34:47,400
 i onda postaje ti mali bijegov i, ok, tome djete treba

753
00:34:47,400 --> 00:34:48,680
 i tome žena treba.

754
00:34:50,480 --> 00:34:52,940
 I zato se još malo krije, gledaj, nisam opće sposoban,

755
00:34:52,940 --> 00:34:55,380
 ne želim se trenutno baviti evangelizacijom.

756
00:34:55,380 --> 00:34:57,080
 I to je isto normalno, ok.

757
00:34:57,080 --> 00:35:02,920
 I nakon trećeg, četvrtog djeteta,

758
00:35:02,920 --> 00:35:04,240
 u nekim slučajima,

759
00:35:04,240 --> 00:35:06,660
 sad nam se vraćaju,

760
00:35:06,660 --> 00:35:08,020
 sad kad je tek teže,

761
00:35:09,120 --> 00:35:12,520
 u slobodi dirnuti ljubavlju,

762
00:35:12,520 --> 00:35:15,660
 dirnuti zdravim pristupom,

763
00:35:15,660 --> 00:35:19,960
 ljudi nam se vraćaju i stavljaju nam se na raspolaganje.

764
00:35:19,960 --> 00:35:22,360
 Stavljaju se, to je, gospodinu na raspolaganje.

765
00:35:22,360 --> 00:35:25,400
 Sad, recimo, trenutno naše stanje u zajednici,

766
00:35:25,400 --> 00:35:27,940
 ne, šestdesetak nas je članova,

767
00:35:27,940 --> 00:35:28,820
 nešto malo više,

768
00:35:29,820 --> 00:35:33,620
 da imamo jednu grupu za mame.

769
00:35:33,620 --> 00:35:36,200
 Imam još malo vremena, pet minuta?

770
00:35:36,200 --> 00:35:38,480
 Imao tako, ok.

771
00:35:38,480 --> 00:35:41,340
 Žena moja se brine, pokazuje na sat,

772
00:35:41,340 --> 00:35:42,220
 evo, doslovno pet.

773
00:35:42,220 --> 00:35:46,620
 Da, pa ona mene pozna,

774
00:35:46,620 --> 00:35:47,920
 ona zna taj strah,

775
00:35:47,920 --> 00:35:49,640
 onda na početku ode u,

776
00:35:49,640 --> 00:35:51,860
 ako mene ne povuče dole.

777
00:35:51,860 --> 00:35:55,800
 Sad imamo grupu za mame,

778
00:35:55,800 --> 00:35:57,960
 žene su se organizirale

779
00:35:57,960 --> 00:36:00,720
 i jednom mjesečnom mole.

780
00:36:00,720 --> 00:36:03,200
 Imaju otvorene susete sa sve druge žene.

781
00:36:03,200 --> 00:36:07,580
 Imamo grupu za djecu do četiri godine,

782
00:36:07,580 --> 00:36:09,940
 gdje se djeca mole.

783
00:36:09,940 --> 00:36:13,700
 Do pete godine grupu od pete godine,

784
00:36:13,700 --> 00:36:15,020
 dječji zbor.

785
00:36:15,020 --> 00:36:17,480
 I uz naše otvorene susete

786
00:36:17,480 --> 00:36:18,960
 imamo obiteljski suset.

787
00:36:18,960 --> 00:36:22,860
 Dakle, sad imamo trenutno vezano za obitelj

788
00:36:22,860 --> 00:36:25,380
 veći sadržaj nego prije.

789
00:36:26,240 --> 00:36:29,640
 Jer sad su u slobodi ljudi došli,

790
00:36:29,640 --> 00:36:31,640
 niko ih nije stiskoo,

791
00:36:31,640 --> 00:36:33,100
 niko im nije dao pritisak

792
00:36:33,100 --> 00:36:34,800
 i to mijenja njihovu,

793
00:36:34,800 --> 00:36:37,460
 to mijenja njihovu sliku o Bogu.

794
00:36:37,460 --> 00:36:38,920
 Kad takav pristup imate.

795
00:36:38,920 --> 00:36:41,220
 I onda u slobodi dolaze,

796
00:36:41,220 --> 00:36:41,640
 kažu,

797
00:36:41,640 --> 00:36:42,500
 evo, gospodine,

798
00:36:42,500 --> 00:36:43,320
 sazrijevaju.

799
00:36:44,600 --> 00:36:46,000
 I evo, za kraj,

800
00:36:46,000 --> 00:36:48,740
 u takvom pristupu,

801
00:36:48,740 --> 00:36:50,680
 kada ulazimo u to iskustvo,

802
00:36:50,680 --> 00:36:51,740
 iz tog iskustva,

803
00:36:51,740 --> 00:36:54,280
 nemoći idemo u tu slobodu,

804
00:36:54,280 --> 00:36:55,400
 postajemo maleni,

805
00:36:55,400 --> 00:36:57,360
 postajemo smireni

806
00:36:57,360 --> 00:37:00,380
 i počinjemo doživljavati čovjeka.

807
00:37:00,380 --> 00:37:02,060
 Kad počneš čovjeka doživljavati

808
00:37:02,060 --> 00:37:03,340
 svakog čovjeka

809
00:37:03,340 --> 00:37:05,600
 jednakom pažnjom i ljubavlju,

810
00:37:05,600 --> 00:37:07,600
 ulazimo,

811
00:37:07,600 --> 00:37:08,480
 ja sam to nazvao,

812
00:37:08,480 --> 00:37:10,040
 u zdravu komunikaciju.

813
00:37:10,040 --> 00:37:12,320
 Znači, zdrava komunikacija

814
00:37:12,320 --> 00:37:14,260
 gdje nema podrazumijevanja.

815
00:37:14,260 --> 00:37:15,180
 Pogledajte,

816
00:37:15,180 --> 00:37:16,720
 možete vidjeti u svojima obiteljima

817
00:37:16,720 --> 00:37:17,780
 koji ste u braku,

818
00:37:17,780 --> 00:37:19,660
 kad ste mužu, žene

819
00:37:19,660 --> 00:37:21,180
 ili muževi,

820
00:37:21,180 --> 00:37:22,760
 kad ste ženama rekli da ih volite.

821
00:37:22,760 --> 00:37:25,340
 Kad ste im rekli hvala ti,

822
00:37:25,340 --> 00:37:27,380
 hvala ti za ovaj ručak,

823
00:37:27,380 --> 00:37:29,360
 hvala ti še si tako dobra mama,

824
00:37:29,360 --> 00:37:30,660
 hvala ti še si moja žena.

825
00:37:30,660 --> 00:37:32,920
 Pa mi to ne govorimo

826
00:37:32,920 --> 00:37:34,260
 nakon nekog vremena

827
00:37:34,260 --> 00:37:35,500
 ili se to podrazumijeva.

828
00:37:35,500 --> 00:37:38,380
 A podrazumijevanje

829
00:37:38,380 --> 00:37:39,420
 ubija ljubav.

830
00:37:39,420 --> 00:37:41,040
 Kad si rekao članu

831
00:37:41,040 --> 00:37:42,020
 svoje zajednice,

832
00:37:42,020 --> 00:37:43,100
 hvala ti,

833
00:37:43,100 --> 00:37:45,560
 hvala ti što si tu sa mnom,

834
00:37:45,560 --> 00:37:46,540
 što te imam,

835
00:37:46,540 --> 00:37:48,060
 tako je lijepo

836
00:37:48,060 --> 00:37:49,640
 s tobom donositi Krista.

837
00:37:49,640 --> 00:37:52,420
 Može da zlučiti očudno,

838
00:37:52,420 --> 00:37:53,880
 mi tako komuniciramo

839
00:37:53,880 --> 00:37:54,680
 sve toj obitelji.

840
00:37:54,680 --> 00:37:56,880
 To je nama prirodno postalo,

841
00:37:56,880 --> 00:37:57,740
 normalno.

842
00:37:57,740 --> 00:38:00,940
 Sine, šta mogu učiniti za tebe?

843
00:38:00,940 --> 00:38:01,880
 Kako ti u školi?

844
00:38:01,960 --> 00:38:02,980
 ili imaš nekih problema?

845
00:38:02,980 --> 00:38:04,540
 Kako ti je sa drugom djecom?

846
00:38:04,540 --> 00:38:06,260
 Dobra komunikacija?

847
00:38:06,260 --> 00:38:08,300
 Kako se osjećaš?

848
00:38:08,300 --> 00:38:09,920
 Bio si na prvom treningu?

849
00:38:09,920 --> 00:38:11,280
 Je li sve bilo ok?

850
00:38:11,280 --> 00:38:13,100
 Ili imaš osjećaja

851
00:38:13,100 --> 00:38:14,420
 da nisi dobar?

852
00:38:14,420 --> 00:38:15,240
 Je li te to muči?

853
00:38:16,680 --> 00:38:17,580
 Znate što se događa?

854
00:38:17,580 --> 00:38:17,580
 Znate što se događa?

855
00:38:17,580 --> 00:38:18,560
 Povratna reakcija.

856
00:38:18,560 --> 00:38:20,080
 Sin u prvom razredu,

857
00:38:20,080 --> 00:38:21,220
 Rafija sa drugi razred,

858
00:38:21,220 --> 00:38:22,820
 dolazi do mene i dane,

859
00:38:22,820 --> 00:38:25,820
 ovakvim načinom našeg obiteljske komunikacije,

860
00:38:25,820 --> 00:38:28,300
 formiranje na taj način i kaže,

861
00:38:28,300 --> 00:38:30,620
 čuj, tate, mama,

862
00:38:30,620 --> 00:38:32,420
 imam jednu situaciju,

863
00:38:32,420 --> 00:38:33,700
 treba mi vaš savjet, kaže.

864
00:38:35,660 --> 00:38:36,720
 Ego, reci sine,

865
00:38:36,720 --> 00:38:39,680
 pa evo, ne znam kak se postaviti u tom, tom i tom.

866
00:38:39,680 --> 00:38:41,300
 I sad nama nabraja.

867
00:38:41,300 --> 00:38:44,940
 Mi kao roditelji do suza budemo ganuti,

868
00:38:44,940 --> 00:38:46,020
 zahvalni Bogu,

869
00:38:46,020 --> 00:38:47,640
 jer vidimo Bog je živ

870
00:38:47,640 --> 00:38:50,880
 i dobro vodi naš obitelj.

871
00:38:50,880 --> 00:38:53,980
 Ta zdrava komunikacija nosi mnogo bodova,

872
00:38:53,980 --> 00:38:55,820
 nosi mnogo blagoslova.

873
00:38:55,820 --> 00:38:57,480
 Taj život u obitelji,

874
00:38:57,480 --> 00:38:58,920
 kad i žrvni obitelji,

875
00:38:58,920 --> 00:39:01,600
 kad smo poravnati s Božijom voljom,

876
00:39:01,600 --> 00:39:04,540
 da tu umirem do kraja,

877
00:39:04,620 --> 00:39:05,900
 iz toga idem van,

878
00:39:05,900 --> 00:39:08,020
 iz stadičkih svojih dužnosti,

879
00:39:08,020 --> 00:39:10,340
 to je kao na onom ispitu,

880
00:39:10,340 --> 00:39:11,540
 nekom stručnom,

881
00:39:11,540 --> 00:39:15,580
 imate jedno pitanje donosi pet bodova,

882
00:39:15,580 --> 00:39:17,760
 a jedno pitanje donosi deset bodova.

883
00:39:17,760 --> 00:39:20,060
 I nama nekad pitamo se

884
00:39:20,060 --> 00:39:21,580
 šta nam fali evangelizaciju,

885
00:39:21,580 --> 00:39:22,820
 ne imamo dovoljno bodova,

886
00:39:22,820 --> 00:39:24,060
 blagoslova do kraja.

887
00:39:24,060 --> 00:39:28,180
 A evo, tu se kriju ti dodatni bodovi,

888
00:39:28,180 --> 00:39:28,940
 blagoslovi.

889
00:39:28,940 --> 00:39:31,080
 Obitelje,

890
00:39:33,580 --> 00:39:37,040
 kad počnemo se njoj davati,

891
00:39:37,040 --> 00:39:38,180
 živjeti za nju,

892
00:39:38,180 --> 00:39:40,540
 obitelj je sigurno utočište.

893
00:39:40,540 --> 00:39:42,580
 Kraljstvo Božje je među nama,

894
00:39:42,580 --> 00:39:44,920
 mjesto gdje postaje

895
00:39:44,920 --> 00:39:46,580
 najbolja verzija sebe,

896
00:39:46,580 --> 00:39:48,120
 gdje smijem bit slab

897
00:39:48,120 --> 00:39:49,880
 i nisam degradiran,

898
00:39:49,880 --> 00:39:51,600
 nek sam i dalje voljen,

899
00:39:51,600 --> 00:39:53,620
 gdje mogu biti onda

900
00:39:53,620 --> 00:39:55,620
 pravo jak.

901
00:39:56,740 --> 00:39:57,940
 i evo,

902
00:39:57,940 --> 00:39:59,880
 samo još misla za one koji imaju djecu,

903
00:39:59,880 --> 00:40:03,200
 kad ono,

904
00:40:03,200 --> 00:40:05,820
 uđem u naviku odbijanja djece,

905
00:40:05,820 --> 00:40:06,600
 da nemoj sad,

906
00:40:06,600 --> 00:40:06,900
 da je ovo,

907
00:40:06,900 --> 00:40:08,400
 ili brzo mu nešto odgovorim,

908
00:40:08,400 --> 00:40:09,980
 ne sa zanimanjem,

909
00:40:12,200 --> 00:40:12,920
 svijetite se,

910
00:40:12,920 --> 00:40:15,440
 da Bog vam

911
00:40:15,440 --> 00:40:17,160
 kroz djecu pokazuje

912
00:40:17,160 --> 00:40:18,340
 koliko ste posebni,

913
00:40:18,340 --> 00:40:19,220
 koliko vas voli.

914
00:40:21,020 --> 00:40:24,800
 djeca idu sa takvim zanimanjem prema vama

915
00:40:24,800 --> 00:40:27,120
 i kad bi smo mi

916
00:40:27,120 --> 00:40:31,680
 sa takvom čežnjom išli prema Bogu,

917
00:40:31,680 --> 00:40:33,480
 kao što djeca idu prema nama,

918
00:40:33,480 --> 00:40:37,160
 o kako bi imali čudesan odnos sa gospodinom.

919
00:40:37,160 --> 00:40:41,760
 Kako bi imali čudesan odnos sa gospodinom.

920
00:40:41,760 --> 00:40:43,000
 Zato evo,

921
00:40:43,000 --> 00:40:45,000
 dajte svoje djeci koji imate

922
00:40:45,000 --> 00:40:47,040
 dan djece pažnju,

923
00:40:47,040 --> 00:40:48,740
 koju zavrijeđuju

924
00:40:48,740 --> 00:40:51,480
 i vidjet ćete kakve će gospodin

925
00:40:51,480 --> 00:40:53,140
 činiti stvari.

926
00:40:53,140 --> 00:40:55,580
 Evo, hvala vam.

